@startuml
title Catalog-to-Cart Workflow
autonumber

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20

actor Customer
participant "Web Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Catalog API\n(/api/v1/catalog)" as CatalogApi
participant "Cart API\n(/api/v1/cart)" as CartApi
participant "Checkout API\n(/api/v1/checkout)" as CheckoutApi
participant "Catalog Service" as CatalogSvc
participant "Cart Service" as CartSvc
participant "Checkout Service" as CheckoutSvc
participant "Reservation Service\n(Redis/Lua)" as ReservationSvc
database "product / product_item /\nproduct_variation" as ProductDb
database "cart / cart_product" as CartDb
database "reservation keys (Redis)" as Redis

== Browse Products ==
Customer -> Frontend : Open product listing
Frontend -> CatalogApi : GET /catalog/products?filters...
CatalogApi -> CatalogSvc : getProducts(query)
CatalogSvc -> ProductDb : load published products + variants
ProductDb --> CatalogSvc : product rows
CatalogSvc --> CatalogApi : normalized product payload
CatalogApi --> Frontend : list response

== View Product Detail ==
Customer -> Frontend : Select product
Frontend -> CatalogApi : GET /catalog/products/{slug}
CatalogApi -> CatalogSvc : getProductDetail(slug)
CatalogSvc -> ProductDb : load product + items + variations
ProductDb --> CatalogSvc : detail rows
CatalogSvc --> CatalogApi : detailed payload
CatalogApi --> Frontend : detail response

== Add Item to Cart ==
Customer -> Frontend : Add selected variation
Frontend -> CartApi : POST /cart/add
CartApi -> CartSvc : addToCart(userId, variationId, qty)
CartSvc -> ProductDb : validate variation + stock
ProductDb --> CartSvc : variant data

alt Stock not enough or invalid variation
  CartSvc --> CartApi : validation error
  CartApi --> Frontend : add-to-cart failed
else Stock valid
  CartSvc -> CartDb : get/create active cart
  CartSvc -> CartDb : insert/update cart_product
  CartSvc -> CartDb : rebuild cart snapshot totals
  CartDb --> CartSvc : updated cart state
  CartSvc --> CartApi : cart snapshot
  CartApi --> Frontend : add-to-cart success
end

== Update/Remove Cart Item ==
Customer -> Frontend : Update qty or remove item
Frontend -> CartApi : PATCH/DELETE cart item
CartApi -> CartSvc : updateCartItemQuantity/removeCartItem
CartSvc -> ProductDb : re-check stock when needed
CartSvc -> CartDb : persist change + recalc totals
CartDb --> CartSvc : updated cart snapshot
CartSvc --> CartApi : operation result
CartApi --> Frontend : refreshed cart

== Checkout Preview and Reservation Setup ==
Customer -> Frontend : Proceed to checkout
Frontend -> CheckoutApi : POST /checkout/preview
CheckoutApi -> CheckoutSvc : buildPreview(userId, cartId)
CheckoutSvc -> CartDb : load active cart items
CartDb --> CheckoutSvc : cart lines
CheckoutSvc -> ProductDb : load latest stock + prices
ProductDb --> CheckoutSvc : validation data
CheckoutSvc -> ReservationSvc : reserve(stock, voucher, ttl)
ReservationSvc -> Redis : execute atomic Lua script
Redis --> ReservationSvc : reservation_token + expiry

alt Reservation failed
  ReservationSvc --> CheckoutSvc : failed(reason)
  CheckoutSvc --> CheckoutApi : checkout blocked
  CheckoutApi --> Frontend : show out-of-stock/limit message
else Reservation succeeded
  ReservationSvc --> CheckoutSvc : reservation_token
  CheckoutSvc --> CheckoutApi : preview + token + expiry
  CheckoutApi --> Frontend : ready for payment
end

@enduml
